            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6fc3a9 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-2ecd31 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6fc3a9 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-2ecd31 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\"><a></a> <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000000093\">[301]</$link> A stang is a pole or perch; sixteen feet and a half.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6fc3a9 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-2ecd31 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6fc3a9 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-2ecd31 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\"><a></a> <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000000217\">[330]</$link> An act of parliament has been since passed by which some breaches of trust have been made capital.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6fc3a9 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-2ecd31 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
