            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/91087f822f8259a9/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6fc3a9 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-2ecd31 twpub-91087f822f8259a9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c2\">Project Gutenberg™ is synonymous with the free distribution of electronic works in formats readable by the widest variety of computers including obsolete, old, middle-aged and new computers. It exists because of the efforts of hundreds of volunteers and donations from people in all walks of life.</div></div>"
        },
